  "name": "RPlog_Fleming_Tortures_Brandis",
  "title": "Fleming Tortures Brandis",
  "summary": "In the detention block of the Star Destroyer Predator, the captured Jedi Kitterick Brandis Finian, kidnapped from an independent world, is handed over by Darth Malign to ISB Agent Korynn Fleming for interrogation, with Dr. Caiton overseeing. Provoked by Brandis's defiance, Malign first unleashes a surge of Dark Side energy that blinds the Jedi and leaves him screaming on the floor before departing. Fleming then has Brandis bound spread-eagled, confirms his blindness with a glow-lamp, and injects a nerve-bonding compound, applying escalating electrical torture while demanding the Jedi answer only to the designation 'Prisoner 2-1-69-Gamma.' Brandis, sublimating the agony through the Force and wrestling against the temptation of the dark side, refuses to break, insisting on his name and his chosen path. Recognizing his standard procedures will not work on a Jedi, Fleming escalates to sensory deprivation therapy, sealing Brandis into a device that strips away all touch, sound, taste, and smell save an endless modulating buzz, leaving him to endure the void indefinitely.",
